{"title":"海堤上的老人","authors":["孙昕晨"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海堤上的老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙昕晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬日的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如你温情的眸子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盐蒿、苦艾、茅草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有翻飞的芦花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西黄海广阔的滩涂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片枯黄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺在你的脚下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海堤是一种高度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使你极目远眺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丹顶鹤、小天鹅、鹭鸶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者是点点银帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色的精灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让你想起家乡六月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炽热如火的骄阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起浓荫里的喜鹊窝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一片叽叽喳喳的绿色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微风在你和树苗之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在铁锹和手臂之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传送着新土的气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一种很好闻的气息啊）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你捋了捋额上的白发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而汗水正流过你的皱纹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛年轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后是沉默的陆地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前方是激动的大海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜿蜒的海堤啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会在树的指引下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找到碧绿的春天"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}